sigkdd#Hotel: The hotel is the child of the conferencehall.
sigkdd#Place: The main office is the parent of the hotel and the conferencehall.
sigkdd#Abstract: The abstract is a child of the document which is the parent of the review.
sigkdd#Document: The document review is the parent of the abstract and the document paper.
sigkdd#Deadline_Abstract_Submission: The deadline for abstract submission is the child of the deadline and the parent of the deadlineauthornotification.
sigkdd#Best_Applications_Paper_Award: bestapplicationspaperaward is a child of award which is parented by bestresearchpaperaward.
sigkdd#Award: bestapplicationspaperaward is the parent of bestresearchpaperaward and beststudentpaperaward.
sigkdd#Deadline_Paper_Submission: The deadline for paper submission is the child of the deadline and the parent of the deadlineauthornotification.
sigkdd#Deadline: The deadline for submitting a paper is the parent of the deadlineauthornotification and the deadlineabstractsubmission.
sigkdd#Deadline_Author_notification: The deadlineauthornotification is the child of the deadline and is the parent of the deadlinepapersubmission.
sigkdd#Webmaster: The webmaster is the child of the programchair and the organizer.
sigkdd#Organizator: The parent of the programcommitteemember is the generalchair. The other two are the organizingcommitteemember and the child of the webmaster.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper_student: The author of paper is the child of the author who is the parent of the author.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Award: beststudentpaperaward is a child of award which is parented by bestapplicationspaperaward.
sigkdd#Author: The author is the child of the speaker, the invited speaker and the author of paper (student).
sigkdd#ACM_SIGKDD: acmsigkdd is a child of Thing.
sigkdd#Sponzor: sponzors are the parents of bronzesupporter and beststudentpapersupporter. They are also the parents of silversupporter and platinumsupporter.
sigkdd#Exhibitor: The exhibitor is the child of the sponsor and the parent of the bronzesupporter.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGMOD_Member: sponzorfee is the parent of registrationfee which is the child of registrationsigmodmember.
sigkdd#Registration_fee: Registrationfee is the parent of registrationstudent and registrationnonmember. It is also the parent of registrationsigmodmember and registrationsigkddmember. It is also the child of registrationfee and sponzorfee.
sigkdd#Person: The parent of the listener and the invited speaker is the listener. The webmaster and the speaker are also the parents of the speaker.
sigkdd#Bronze_Supporter: The bronzesupporter is the child of sponzor and silversupporter.
sigkdd#Committee: The committee is the parent of the organizingcommittee, the programcommittee and the bestpaperawardscommittee.
sigkdd#Platinum_Supporter: The platinumsupporter is the child of sponzor and bronzesupporter.
sigkdd#Conference_hall: The conferencehall is the child of the hotel.
sigkdd#Best_Paper_Awards_Committee: The bestpaperawardscommittee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the organizingcommittee.
sigkdd#Program_Chair: The programchair is the child of the programcommittee member and the programchair is the parent of the programcommittee member.
sigkdd#Main_office: The main office is the child of the hotel.
sigkdd#Registration_Non-Member: registrationfee is a child of registrationfee which is a child of registrationfee.
sigkdd#Fee: The registrationfee is the parent of the registrationstudent and the sponzorfee.
sigkdd#Review: Review is a child of document which is parented by paper.
sigkdd#Sponzor_fee: sponzorfee is child of fee which is parented by registrationfee and registrationsigmodmember.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGKDD_Member: The registrationsigkddmember is the child of registrationfee which is the parent of sponzorfee.
sigkdd#Program_Committee: The programcommittee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the organizingcommittee.
sigkdd#General_Chair: The generalchair is the child of the programchair and the organizer.
sigkdd#Speaker: Author of PaperStudent is the parent of the speaker who is the child of the listener and the invited speaker. The author of PaperStudent is also the parent of the speaker.
sigkdd#Gold_Supporter: Goldsupporter is the child of sponzor and silversupporter.
sigkdd#Registration_Student: The registrationstudent is a child of the registrationfee who is the parent of the registrationsigmodmember.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee: The organizingcommittee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the bestpaperawardscommittee.
sigkdd#Listener: The listener is a child of the speaker and the author of paper. The author is the parent of the speaker.
sigkdd#Program_Committee_member: The programcommitteemember is a child of the programchair and the organizer.
sigkdd#Invited_Speaker: The invited speaker is a child of the speaker.
sigkdd#Best_Research_Paper_Award: The bestresearchpaperaward is the child of the award and the parent of the beststudentpaperaward.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Supporter: beststudentpapersupporter is the child of sponzor who is the parent of bronzesupporter.
sigkdd#Paper: The paper is the child of the document which is the parent of the review.
sigkdd#Silver_Supporter: The silversupporter is the child of sponzor and bronzesupporter.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee_member: The organizingcommitteemember is the child of the organizer and the speaker. The invited speaker is also the parent of the speaker.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper: The author of paper is the child of the author and the parent of the author ofpaperstudent.
